Benoît Régent https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Beno%C3%AEt_R%C3%A9gent 0 Benoît Régent (19 August 1953 – 21 October 1994) was a French actor. He was born in Nantes. He died at the age of 41 of a ruptured aneurysm in Zürich, Switzerland. Benoît_Régent ( 19_August_1953 – 21_October_1994 ) was a_French_actor . He was_born in Nantes .
